# Assets Loans And Advances Other ARF117 Amount

## identifier
de8198

## type
float

## definition
This is a balancing item in the list in which it is being used.

This is the value, as at the relevant date, of other loans and advances, as required on form ARF_117_0 and represents loans and advances other than those classified as:
     - Revolving credit;
     - Credit cards;
     - Housing loans;
     - Term loans; and
     - Lease financing.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.LoansAndAdvancesOtherARF117.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=instant
